extendedInfo.description: Engineering College Finder from Guide for Engineers is all about making life simple and easy for thousands of students who are aspiring to be future engineers. Todayâs mobile technology has given students so much power to make decision that it has become indispensable part of their lives. Choosing the right engineering college take meticulous research and plenty of time this is where you can make use of our College Finder to save time and locate best colleges around you. If you know your MH-CET marks then all you have to do is launch the app, enter your Name, Marks, Phone Number, Stream and University to get the result.  This app offers you details of the colleges you are looking for along with cut-off list of previous year, college ratings, directions to get there and courses offered by each of them. Currently this app works only for Maharashtra state universities and we are working hard to add more states in the near future. We regularly keep on updating latest data to this app so that you always stay ahead in finding the best colleges. Benefits of using Engineering College Finder1. Search colleges based on your MH-CET marks, stream, and university.2. View detail of various colleges and their cut-off list of the previous year3. You can compare colleges as per various criteria.4. Get details about the colleges- their ratings, description, contact info, address, e-mail and courses offered.5. Save time and stay aheadEngineering College Finder is supported on all Android devices. For further details please do visit our website www.guideforengineers.com
